Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.mime

Class ContentID

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.mime.ContentID
public final class ContentID extends Object
A MIME content-id or RFC 5322 msg-id value. This corresponds to the msg-id production in RFC 5322 section 3.6.4 and the id production in RFC 2045 section 7 (Content-ID). The format is <id-left@id-right>.
Author:
Chris Burdess
